      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Good-condition car that presents well overall and appears to have been kept up with care. The paint, interior, and general presentation are all solid, with the kind of light cosmetic wear, minor blemishes, and age-related signs of use you would expect from a well-maintained driver rather than a mint example. It should suit a buyer looking for an attractive, enjoyable car they can use and show with confidence, while understanding it is not flawless and may have some typical minor needs consistent with age and regular use.",
