      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that shows well and should make a solid driver for its next owner. The body and paint present nicely overall with the kind of normal age-related cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect on a well-kept older vehicle, and the interior is tidy and usable without pretending to be concours or mint. Trim, finishes, and overall presentation are respectable, making this a car you can enjoy as-is while continuing to improve if you want. A good, straightforward car for someone looking for a nice example without paying top-of-market mint-condition money.",
