      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid candidate for an enthusiast build or budget driver project. This car presents in poor overall condition, but it appears largely complete and offers a good mechanical starting point for someone who knows their way around maintenance and sorting work. The chassis has honest wear, and it\u2019s best approached as a repair/refresh opportunity, yet it still has the kind of usable bones that make these worth saving. Great fit for a buyer looking for an affordable entry point, parts donor with potential, or a hands-on restoration project. Priced to move for someone ready to put in the work.",
